messages.message: I’ve also written a document detailing the steps that are needed to add a new step to flow: https://docs.google.com/document/d/18QUZH9sjv3l2CYx29BbbvrxaGWCDmNkWwgKFRMj9gXI/edit?usp=sharing. It’s still a WIP, but currently details the steps needed to get it working for Flow V2 Batch. Hopefully, this also shows why we need to refactor flow so badly lol.
